/target
test_snapshots/
**/*.rs.bk
.cargo/

# Cargo.lock is NOT ignored on purpose: pinning transitive deps
# (notably `ed25519-dalek 2.1.1` to work around `soroban-env-host 22.1.3`'s
# incompatible build with `ed25519-dalek 3.0`) lets CI use `cargo
# test --locked` for deterministic, reproducible builds.
